data.description: This beautifully well maintained 1 bed / 1bath condo boasts 10-foot ceilings, crown molding, granite countertops, wood and tile flooring, an extra study/bunk room and laundry room in the amenity rich community of Island Reserve. The current owners have updated the kitchen appliances, cabinets, carpet, paint and have scheduled plantation shutters to be installed before closing. The private balcony has a wonderful view of the courtyard and pool, the perfect place to relax and take in the beautiful surroundings while listening to the nearby soothing water fountain. The community offers a 100'' theater screen room, fitness center, volleyball court, indoor basketball court and an incredible 1-acre resort style pool with waterfall. This unit won't last long so call today to schedule a showing!
